==Yiddish==
===verb===
# to travel or to cross, as in the folk song "Kum Aher, Du Filozof:"
:A dampfshif hostu oysgetrakht un nemst dermit zikh iber;
:Der rebbe shpreyt zayn tikhl oys un shpant dem yam ariber.

Which has the English translation:
:The steamship you've invented so you think you're something big, 
:but the rabbi waves his handkerchief and crosses the Atlantic instantly.

